{"title": "Um punho fraco fechado para seu parceiro Rosa", "published time": "2024-03-02T00-00-00-01-00", "images": ["https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhvRnwnRwa26gNBHJjGhvXMxQPymrJXoiszL73BFhc_lXCdQkrsTJp_s1Y2SSUKTIZho-T79js2hm8XAI_KkwGAa4UfxElEQ2z9aua4Y3G9huwkVUjgHHG-EYoyXpC8wksaPVrKCnSUmXBUzg9Ai_m8d9s5cva0VKkG55ZFQkWkYD-M54IE6u5KNI3geNaY/s1024/425331143_383422234440105_6217278629396226349_n.jpeg"], "content": "<div class=\"post-body entry-content\" id=\"post-body-7018638048831869402\" itemprop=\"description articleBody\"><div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 6px;\"><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">A parceira Rosa Calderazzi morreu por algum tempo</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Ruim, com momentos curtos de melhoria. De 24/2, foi hospitalizado para</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">San.raffaele e aqui falhou.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Rosa h\u00e1 muitos anos estava participando e participando das iniciativas,</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Mobiliza\u00e7\u00f5es n\u00e3o de menos de Mil\u00e3o, mas tamb\u00e9m para as assembl\u00e9ias e</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Eventos nacionais de NUDM; Assim como ele freq\u00fcentou e deu o seu pr\u00f3prio</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Apoio \u00e0s iniciativas dom\u00e9sticas femininas.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Ativo, participante, proativo, desde o ver\u00e3o de 68, em</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">particular em Mil\u00e3o, ele n\u00e3o perdeu seu compromisso antes</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Uni\u00e3o como um trabalhador do Proveveditorato para estudos em Mil\u00e3o,</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">portanto, pol\u00edtico, cultural e luta nos anos seguintes at\u00e9</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">H\u00e1 pouco tempo.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Ele estava acima de tudo feliz que sua atividade estava junto com mulheres,</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">para companheiros.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Aqueles que a conheciam, a apreciavam, que a amavam, se</span><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Eles querem, eles ser\u00e3o capazes de cumpriment\u00e1 -la.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">A fun\u00e7\u00e3o secular para se despedir de Rosa ser\u00e1 realizada no s\u00e1bado, 2 de mar\u00e7o, \u00e0s 15h, na sala multifuncional dentro do cemit\u00e9rio de Lambrate, em Mil\u00e3o.</span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"/><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\">Irm\u00e3 de Rosa, Margherita</span></div><div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 6px;\"><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\"><br/></span></div><div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 6px;\"><span face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #222222;\"><br/></span></div><div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 6px;\"><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1024\" data-original-width=\"768\" height=\"320\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-02T00-00-00-01-00/000000.jpeg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-02T00-00-00-01-00/000000.jpeg\" width=\"240\"/></div><div style='color: #1c1e21; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \".SFNSText-Regular\", sans-serif;'><div class=\"x1cy8zhl x78zum5 x1q0g3np xod5an3 x1pi30zi x1swvt13 xz9dl7a\" style=\"align-items: flex-start; display: flex; flex-direction: row; font-family: inherit; margin-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-top: 12px;\"><div class=\"x1iyjqo2\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; font-family: inherit;\"><div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xz62fqu x16ldp7u\" style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; font-family: inherit; margin-bottom: -5px; margin-top: -5px;\"><div class=\"xu06os2 x1ok221b\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span class=\"x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xlh3980 xvmahel x1n0sxbx x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x4zkp8e x3x7a5m x1f6kntn xvq8zen xo1l8bm xi81zsa x1yc453h\" color=\"var(--secondary-text)\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; font-family: inherit;  line-height: 1.3333; max-width: 100%; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word;\"><h3 class=\"x1heor9g x1qlqyl8 x1pd3egz 